strings.Value: {n}Ntavi's face is covered with giants' blood. She licks her lips hungrily.{/n} "Mmm, what can be sweeter than vengeance... Remember this feeling, Ekun. And when spirits of the dead disturb your peace again, the ever-burning flame in your chest will tell you what to do."

"I would love to stay... and pay a visit to Elina to teach her to keep her mouth shut... but a priestess of {g|Calistria}Calistria{/g} always has things to do. Farewell, Ekun! And don't forget your old friend Ntavi... at least this time." {n}Ntavi's low laughter echoes around you, then fades.{/n}
"I didn't know she became a priestess. She's changed."
{n}Ekun looks exhausted.{/n} "Thanks for your help, {name}. I feel... better. Let us speak again when we reach the capital."
